Package: silcc
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: Consistant Changes
 Consistent Changes is useful for finding all occurrences of specified
 characters, words, or phrases in a text file or series of text files, and
 then changing them in a consistent way.

